Red Lion Inns LimitedPartnership said it declared an initial cash distribution of 43cts per unit, which is a proration of 50 cts per quarter.    The distribution is payable August 14 to unitholders ofrecord June 30.    The payout was adjusted to reflect the actual number ofdays the partnership will have owned the hotels during thecalendar quarter ended June 30, 1987. Reuter&#3;